desc: Welcome to Cecile Raley Designs. Custom make your own jewelry and find some gorgeous and unique gemstones. Create your own special piece of jewelry from scratch or by choosing a piece from our catalog and adding gemstones from our shop. We may also be able to source something for you if you can't find what you need.

layout.text: Visit our shop on Etsy for a selection of ready-to-ship and ready-to-wear fine jewelry.
